title: LAP: Chinese Immigrants in Mexico
description: Tomas Ocampo, Outreach Coordinator for Latin American Perspectives, interviews an associate editor of the journal, Tamar Diana Wilson, about her comments of her research on "Chinese Immigrants in Mexico."
